IntenseLogic - game engine

Usage:
    il [--run=SCRIPT] [--logfile=FILE] [--path=PATH]
    il -h | --help | --version

Options:
  -h, --help             Show this screen.
  -r, --run SCRIPT       Runs script
  -l, --logfile	FILE     Sets the file to print output to
  -p, --path PATH        Adds an asset search path
  -t, --threads NUM      Sets the number of worker threads
  -v, --verbose	LEVEL    Sets the verbosity level [default: 4]
